text: Gabriella Sciolti is an Italian water polo player. She was a member of the Italian women's national water polo team. She played for the 2001 World Aquatics Championships. and 2001 Women's European Water Polo Championship. == References == == Other websites == * Gabriella Sciolti appende la calottina, Il Piccolo 2011-2-18 Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Living people Category:Italian water polo players
